---
title: HelloHero: Double Roast Lamb Rump & Salsa Verde  with Garlicky Potatoes & Slaw
description: This is a dazzling twist on a classic Sunday roast with all the trimmings. Lamb rump, cooked to pinky perfection, golden spiced
potatoes, a zingy salsa verde and crunchy slaw. Is your mouth watering yet? Time to get this in the oven!
